statements: SELECT * FROM OutreachMetrics WHERE id = 1;
SELECT strategy_name, response_rate FROM OutreachMetrics WHERE conversion_rate > 0.5;
SELECT id, response_rate, conversion_rate FROM OutreachMetrics WHERE strategy_name = 'Email Campaign';
SELECT * FROM OutreachMetrics ORDER BY response_rate DESC;
SELECT strategy_name, conversion_rate FROM OutreachMetrics ORDER BY strategy_name ASC, conversion_rate DESC;
SELECT * FROM OutreachMetrics WHERE response_rate > 0.5 ORDER BY strategy_name DESC;
SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_records FROM OutreachMetrics;
SELECT strategy_name, AVG(conversion_rate) AS avg_conversion_rate FROM OutreachMetrics GROUP BY strategy_name HAVING AVG(conversion_rate) > 0.1;
SELECT MAX(response_rate) AS max_response_rate FROM OutreachMetrics;
SELECT strategy_name, SUM(response_rate) AS total_response_rate FROM OutreachMetrics GROUP BY strategy_name ORDER BY total_response_rate DESC;
SELECT * FROM outreach_strategies;
SELECT strategy_id, strategy_name FROM outreach_strategies ORDER BY strategy_id DESC;
SELECT strategy_name, response_rate, conversion_rate FROM outreach_strategies WHERE response_rate > 0.5;
SELECT strategy_name, response_date, responses_received FROM outreach_results ORDER BY response_date ASC;
SELECT * FROM outreach_results WHERE conversions >= 10 ORDER BY responses_received DESC;
SELECT strategy_id, strategy_name, response_rate, conversion_rate FROM outreach_strategies WHERE response_rate > 0.5 ORDER BY conversion_rate DESC;
SELECT strategy_name, response_rate, conversion_rate FROM outreach_strategies WHERE conversion_rate < 0.4 ORDER BY response_rate ASC;
SELECT result_id, strategy_id, response_date, responses_received, conversions FROM outreach_results WHERE strategy_id = 3 ORDER BY response_date DESC;
SELECT strategy_name, response_rate, conversion_rate FROM outreach_strategies WHERE response_rate BETWEEN 0.3 AND 0.6;
SELECT * FROM outreach_results WHERE conversions > 100 ORDER BY responses_received DESC;
SELECT * FROM outreach_strategies;
SELECT strategy_name, response_rate FROM outreach_strategies ORDER BY response_rate DESC;
SELECT strategy_name, conversion_rate FROM outreach_strategies WHERE conversion_rate > 0.5;
SELECT response_date, response_content FROM responses WHERE strategy_id = 1;
SELECT * FROM conversions ORDER BY conversion_date DESC;
SELECT strategy_name, response_rate FROM outreach_strategies;
SELECT * FROM responses WHERE response_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT response_content FROM responses WHERE strategy_id = 1 ORDER BY response_date DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT strategy_name, conversion_value FROM outreach_strategies JOIN conversions ON outreach_strategies.id = conversions.strategy_id WHERE conversion_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31';

SELECT strategy_name AS Strategy, AVG(conversion_value) AS Average_Conversion FROM outreach_strategies JOIN conversions ON outreach_strategies.id = conversions.strategy_id GROUP BY strategy_name HAVING AVG(conversion_value) > 5000;
SELECT * FROM outreach_strategies;
SELECT strategy_name, response_rate FROM outreach_strategies WHERE strategy_id = 1;
SELECT strategy_name, start_date, end_date FROM outreach_strategies ORDER BY start_date DESC;
SELECT strategy_name, conversion_rate FROM outreach_strategies WHERE end_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM campaign_metrics WHERE clicks > 100 ORDER BY conversions DESC;
SELECT * FROM outreach_strategies WHERE response_rate > 10.00
SELECT strategy_name, start_date, end_date FROM outreach_strategies ORDER BY start_date DESC
SELECT * FROM audience_feedback WHERE strategy_id = 3
SELECT strategy_id, campaign_date, impressions, clicks FROM campaign_metrics WHERE impressions >= 1000 AND clicks >= 500
SELECT strategy_id, response_status, conversion_status FROM performance_tracking WHERE response_status = TRUE
SELECT * FROM outreach_strategies ORDER BY response_rate DESC;
SELECT strategy_name, conversion_rate FROM outreach_strategies WHERE response_rate > 0.5;
SELECT email_address, sent_date FROM emails_sent WHERE strategy_id = 1 ORDER BY sent_date ASC LIMIT 10;
SELECT response_type, response_date FROM responses_received WHERE response_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-06-30';
SELECT strategy_id, success FROM campaign_results WHERE result_date = '2022-08-15';
SELECT * FROM outreach_strategies WHERE id = 1;
SELECT strategy_name, response_rate FROM outreach_strategies WHERE conversion_rate > 0.5 ORDER BY strategy_name;
SELECT es.email_address, rr.response_type, c.conversion_type FROM emails_sent es JOIN responses_received rr ON es.id = rr.email_id JOIN conversions c ON rr.id = c.response_id;
SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_emails_sent, AVG(response_rate) AS average_response_rate FROM outreach_strategies os JOIN emails_sent es ON os.id = es.strategy_id;

SELECT cr.result_date, COUNT(*) AS total_success FROM campaign_results cr JOIN outreach_strategies os ON cr.strategy_id = os.id WHERE success = TRUE GROUP BY cr.result_date ORDER BY cr.result_date DESC;
